headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  GALLAGHER, WILLIAM D.

snippet: GALLAGHER--William D.,of McMahon Martine and Gallagher. Passed away on February 20 from complications of a stroke. He is survived by his wife Anne their six sons, their wives, his brother, four sisters, nine grandchildren and many nieces and nephews. For full obituary, go to JJFFH.com. 1/3
